{"tid":2459104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"測量師認管有剪鉗 原今判刑唯社服令報告尚未完成 其間准保釋外出","createTime":"2021-03-24T03:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T03:57:28.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5328efc745bc9727034e9b29dd4e8918ea9d6a5e","tid":2459104,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"前年11月理大衝突期間，<span class=\"red\">27歲地盤測量師從理大逃出後</span>，被警員發現躺在旺角東港鐵站往紅磡港鐵站中間路軌明渠上，身上被搜出剪鉗等工具。他早前承認一項管有工具意圖作非法用途罪，還押候判。裁判官<span class=\"red\">鄭念慈</span>下令為其索取社會服務令報告，原定於今日判刑，惟報告仍未完成。鄭官把案件押至4月9日判刑。鄭官認同被告有反省，過去刑事定罪紀錄與本案性質不同，批准被告保釋候判，惟向被告強調<span class=\"red\">此舉不等於會判處非監禁式刑罰</span>。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官沿用被告早前的保釋條件，另要求被告從一星期到警署報到一次增至一星期三次，其餘條件不變。<br />\n<br />\n被告李被控於2019年11月18日，在旺角東港鐵站往紅磡港鐵站中間路軌明渠內，管有一把21厘米長黃色剪鉗。"},{"pid":"cba812174ad0e1feec7355cd33edf645e19f9a00","tid":2459104,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b097549a022b673caa887e3195d373b29c801e94","tid":2459104,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd15b301c6e2e7bb277efce038a4a7719e00442","tid":2459104,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"又認"},{"pid":"ec688c1b83aa6901a457ca4f1cd8fa287e457a49","tid":2459104,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07d970861e763f885382baf5bd252a0fc2f7170","tid":2459104,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"念慈BB 呢輪搞乜"},{"pid":"46d6b6a0ffe97a455e051aba7db4f4aea